{
    "version": "1.85.1",
    "description": "Windows平台的网速监控悬浮窗软件，支持显示网速、CPU/内存利用率、温度监控、任务栏嵌入等功能",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/zhongyang219/TrafficMonitor",
    "license": {
        "identifier": "MIT",
        "url": "https://github.com/zhongyang219/TrafficMonitor/blob/master/LICENSE"
    },
    "url": "https://github.com/zhongyang219/TrafficMonitor/releases/download/V1.85.1/TrafficMonitor_V1.85.1_x64.zip",
    "extract_dir": "TrafficMonitor",
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "bin": "TrafficMonitor.exe",
            "shortcuts": [
                [
                    "TrafficMonitor.exe",
                    "TrafficMonitor (网速监控)",
                    "",
                    "TrafficMonitor.exe"
                ]
            ]
        }
    },
    "pre_install": [
        "if (-not (Test-Path \"$dir\\TrafficMonitor.exe\")) {",
        "    Write-Error \"核心程序文件 TrafficMonitor.exe 缺失，请检查下载包完整性！\"",
        "    exit 1",
        "}"
    ],
    "checkver": "github",
    "autoupdate": {
        "url": "https://github.com/zhongyang219/TrafficMonitor/releases/download/V$version/TrafficMonitor_V$version_x64.zip",
        "extract_dir": "TrafficMonitor"
    },
    "notes": [
        "1. 若启动提示缺少 MSVC*.dll，请安装 Visual C++ 运行库：",
        "   https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-CN/cpp/windows/latest-supported-vc-redist?view=msvc-170",
        "2. 右键悬浮窗可开启任务栏显示、调整监控项等设置",
        "3. 如需无温度监控版本，请手动下载 Lite 版替换程序文件"
    ]
}
